    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m selling my absolute gem of a car and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been my pride and joy, kept meticulously clean and always tucked away in the garage. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feel without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person\u2014come see for yourself! \u2728",
