    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and the original factory scent remains intact. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with the tactile precision of a brand-new vehicle. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service portfolio documenting every fluid change and inspection performed exclusively by certified technicians. The engine bay is detailed to a show-standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of road debris or oxidation. This is a collector-grade investment for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
