    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing high-pressure double VANOS and individual throttle bodies for an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis has been meticulously maintained, featuring documented rear subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry free of bushing compliance. The factory Carbon Black paint retains its deep luster, and the interior Nappa leather shows no bolster wear. A mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
